  "texts": [
    "This potential will allow educators, students, and researchers to be better able to keep pace with the technological advancements, compared to traditional journal articles (Islam & Islam, 2023).",
    "Several studies have examined the power of ChatGPT to improve academic writing.",
    "Macdonald et al. (2023) used ChatGPT to write a research article using a simulated dataset and multiple prompts.",
    "These researchers found that ChatGPT was able to conduct a literature review and generate code using the programming language R to facilitate data analysis.",
    "Macdonald and colleagues then used Chat-GPT to generate a coherent scientific paper that included an introduction, methods, results, and discussion section."
